{"tid":2493510,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"花姐效力TVB 13年直認過檔ViuTV更快樂：原來以前係井底之蛙！","createTime":"2021-04-18T03:32:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T03:40:13.000Z","uid":350584,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5921f4ca4ad14d6006c3af180aa5e7d30dc6c3aa","tid":2493510,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:32:09.000Z","msg":"人稱花姐的黃慧君是現時炙手可熱男團MIRROR、ERROR的幕後推手兼經理人，周五以《尋夢者》為命題接受陳志雲（Stephen）的訪問，談起阿花這個名字的由來，她說身邊的人都不會叫她全名只因曾有算命師傅稱「君」字與她的命格相沖，父母之後都改口叫她阿花。其實花姐的英文名是Ahfa，不過那時無綫（TVB）的同事都不知道怎樣讀，所以都叫她阿花，令Stephen也忍不住揶揄：「算啦，佢哋嘅文化水平係低啲。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPS1oyF3d89uQUw43UqJDfzGGVXgiFbLH11AMiFoFvhPM?filename=1XEqPFa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1XEqPFa.jpg&h=af5fe435&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"151146afc41ed29494cdf71fd096c219f649d092","tid":2493510,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:32:25.000Z","msg":"人稱花姐的黃慧君是現時炙手可熱男團MIRROR、ERROR的幕後推手兼經理人，周五以《尋夢者》為命題接受陳志雲（Stephen）的訪問。（YouTube／＠志雲頻道stephenchannel）"},{"pid":"11b536c8efb8bdb099cdf0e77c92acad7c925e5b","tid":2493510,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:32:47.000Z","msg":"花姐又談起從TVB過檔ViuTV的過程，她說當年離開TVB只是為啖氣：「嗰陣已經做咗《勁歌》一段時間，當時節目換監製，我脾氣差又啱啱升職，覺得自己好叻就同老細嗌交，跟住就走咗。」之後轉職做演唱會導演，由於經常要走埠，那時卻成家立室有了孩子，於是老公希望她穩定下來，金生就介紹她到now TV見工，輾轉展開了ViuTV的監製生涯：「我發現自己唔鍾意安定！」"},{"pid":"4fac8c6d49c3e048d9fa5cbd94b04ec5564feb74","tid":2493510,"uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:33:13.000Z","msg":"花姐亦坦承現時在ViuTV工作，比起在TVB工作的13年更快樂：「嗰時喺TVB做嘢太多框框，原來以前係井底蛙，以為自己識好多嘢，出到嚟就知死喇，原來乜都唔識！」Stephen笑言：「所有TVB人都係咁！因為TVB制度唔同，佢架構大、收視群好多，要冒險少少都難。」花姐及後亦道出深愛ViuTV的原因：「我覺得魯生（ViuTV董事總經理魯庭暉）唔係一個好守規矩嘅人，佢話：『只要你唔令我犯法做咩都得！』」"},{"pid":"4636c0a1f9963b18e7332a0fafb0a3a0f1977ef2","tid":2493510,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXw6hqhdKg8ZaQ9wfzjXnY4GBCThMJoKpRjC7ZC6G85tS?filename=DJeiqex.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJeiqex.jpg&h=61db2872&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49e62f5399f5961e83150294412189458f6e1cd7","tid":2493510,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:35:02.000Z","msg":"花姐其實真係算係咁，依個歲數都同班後生仔打成一片。"},{"pid":"b11275d556df3dbbc18bbb738a102b7228390620","tid":2493510,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVPgTpWk84jGHP4SW6YpW4pYRxgkWg5BhqV7asgWuiEQS?filename=fpzyd8g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffpzyd8g.jpg&h=478c6642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n保錡早前暗撻沙律張沛樂，卻因處理感情不當慘遭網民圍插。（IG：＠charlottecheung107）"},{"pid":"6f5d1b7545046817528481f5f1c0afd87bd11362","tid":2493510,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"49e62f5399f5961e83150294412189458f6e1cd7","tid":2493510,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:35:02.000Z","msg":"花姐其實真係算係咁，依個歲數都同班後生仔打成一片。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:38:26.000Z","msg":"Yes, 同mirror error 打成一片"},{"pid":"d5a28ddb02853bb58396872eeb0840d82d8c3747","tid":2493510,"uid":41342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:38:28.000Z","msg":"睇佢Error遊同error鬥嘴同玩癲野<br />\n覺得佢份人唔假 好實際同肯試新嘢"},{"pid":"62be2fe840c31f62b9cbfd43794f7ecfb84773af","tid":2493510,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5a28ddb02853bb58396872eeb0840d82d8c3747","tid":2493510,"uid":41342,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:38:28.000Z","msg":"睇佢Error遊同error鬥嘴同玩癲野<br />\n覺得佢份人唔假 好實際同肯試新嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:40:13.000Z","msg":"True <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}